      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，仓库模式作为基础设施层。那 Repository 和 RepositoryPatternImplementation 是继承关系还是实现关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Repository",
